  abstract    = {In a distant galaxy a benevolent republic has been
replaced by an oppressive empire. Luke Skywalker, a
farmer's nephew, receives a message recorded by Princess
Leia, a member of the rebel group which seeks the overthrow
of the Empire, who has been captured by the evil Darth
Vader. The message tells him to find Obi Wan Kenobi, an old
Jedi knight. Ben then teaches Luke the Jedi secrets,
particularly concerning the use of The Force. He also
reveals that the orphaned Luke's father had also been a
Jedi knight. They hire Han Solo, a mercenary pilot, and
rescue Leia. Ben is killed by Darth Vader in a duel, but
the others escape. They, and the rebel forces, attack the
Empire's stronghold and win an important victory. The
initially ambivalent Han Solo becomes converted to the
rebel cause.},
