discussed: basic traits of modern technology according to
Jonas, the paradoxical character of the "Baconian
programme", the new dimension of human power and his
dominion over nature, the technological imperative, gnostic
and existentialist influences in the shaping of Jonas's
final view regarding technological determinism.},
