  pages         = {213-235},
  volume        = {56},
  abstract      = {In this paper Hans Jonas's views regarding nihilism,
existentialism and modern technology are presented and
discussed. The impact of Heidegger's thought on Jonas is
also examined. With the help of ideas of Hans Freyer and
