  producer           = {Silver, Joel},
  abstract           = {Science fiction thriller. To save the world of the future,
a software computer expert in modern-day America is brought
into contact with a mysterious character called Morpheus,
the inhabitant of a universe some 2000 years in the future.
The software expert, now rechristened Neo, agrees to be
fitted with technology enabling him to be updated
continuously with endless amounts of knowledge, so that he
can eventually do battle with the Matrix, a power field run
by sinister computer-like forces, that controls a new
"virtual" real world.},
